FOX Football Friday Week Six - KMPH FOX 26 | Central San Joaquin Valley News Source Member Center: FOX Football Friday Week Six Posted: nking@kmph.com FRESNO, Calif. (KMPH) - 
Week six highlights and scores from around the Valley. Highlights include Bullard vs. Madera, Madera South vs. Sanger, Edison vs. Memorial, Clovis vs. Clovis East, Clovis North vs. Clovis West, Chowchilla vs. Kerman, Hoover vs. Fresno and Mt. Whitney vs. Hanford West. Plus, "Sideline Specialist" David Gonzalez, Jr. from Sunnyside.
